name: Dejeuner Du Matin (Breakfast)
description:
He poured the coffee Into the cup,He put the milk Into the cup of coffee ,He put the sugar Into the coffee with milk , With a small spoon , He churned
He drank the coffee and he put down the cup
Without any word to me , His hat on his head He put on
His raincoat Because it was raining
And he left , And I buried
My face in my hands
And I cried ...
